title: Tiago a Través del Tiempo
description: Rogelio De La Vega is Tiago, a time traveler, hero, and lover who visits important moments in history.
quote: Now get over here, Susan B. Anthony, and give me a kiss!
altHero: Tiago as a Frenchman during Marie Antoinette’s reign
alt1: Tiago raises a brick at the Stonewall rebellion
alt2: Tiago as a champion of women’s right to vote
alt4: Tiago as an officer in the CIA
